# hero: the editor on a real SKY130 cell with every panel doing something. Layers
# panel (left), DRC panel with the 11 violations listed, minimap (top right), and the
# properties inspector populated by a selected shape, with that shape's net
# highlighted on the canvas. This still replaces the old canvas-only hero.
viewport 1600x1000
use-case inspect-cell
wait 22
run-drc
wait 4
select 5
highlight-net 5
wait 6
snap hero
